<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Computer Associates reaffirmed.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Computer Associates reaffirmed.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Cowen &amp; Co said analyst Drew Brosseau reiterated a strong buy on Computer Associates International Inc.</p>
<p>-- Company said on Thursday that third quarter revenues would be below Wall Street estimates, due to softness in the European market.</p>
